getSubtype().Description: Returns the subtype of this media track; one of the SUBTYPE_ constants.

getContentId().Description: Returns the content ID of the media track.

setContentId(java.lang.String).Description: Sets the content ID for the media track.

getLanguage().Description: Returns the language of this media track in 6_E@ format, or null if none was specified.

getName().Description: Returns the name of the media track, or null if none was specified.

getContentType().Description: Returns the content type (MIME type) of the media track, or null if none was specified.

getType().Description: Returns the type of the track; one of the TYPE_ constants.

getId().Description: Returns the unique ID of the media track.

setContentType(java.lang.String).Description: Sets the content type (MIME type) of the media track.

getCustomData().Description: Returns the custom data object for this media track, or null if none was specified.

ClassDesc: A class that represents a media track, such as a language track or closed caption text track in a video.
